{"tid":1246852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出左金鐘又唔知做乜好?","createTime":"2019-06-21T01:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:05:44.000Z","uid":62011,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbdd20ee0ce8236476746b145c585b53dba8adb","tid":1246852,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"其實大家無必要對金鐘有情意結，依家敵人根本要避戰，包圍一座無人既建築物做乜姐?  既然佢要避，我地咪唔避俾佢避，一於將戰線拉闊，將呢個抗爭橫向發展。<br />\n<br />\n依家係金鐘集結既有千零人，大家都可以諗下有乜人小而可以表達訴求既方法，有可以make noise。<br />\n<br />\n例如 幾百人係旅遊區(例如金紫荊)閃電式掛bannner(寫上我地訴求)然後走佬；係旅遊區派反送中傳單俾大陸狗。呢d係可以人少，make noise, 俾些小壓力俾商界(其實商界係反送中，唔需要驚影響)。當然群眾智慧係無窮無盡，有人有更好既橋提出就更正啦。"},{"pid":"10a32c55b9a4595e1dc9c95eec0f9632ef3a15c8","tid":1246852,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12456939fc0b917fcecb28c5ed9b9ca68d8370b4","tid":1246852,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af713b50a8664d787652ad49c7a7ab7da5d8540","tid":1246852,"uid":164538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0beb38a3aecdf240ece1af2653fc75db47b801a","tid":1246852,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"今晚梁烈士頭七"}]}